'''2Kill Gaming''' is a Brazilian multi-gaming organization.

== History ==
In 2013, Corsair Brazil founded 2Kill Gaming, a Brazilian organization which has teams in League of Legends, Dota 2, Point Blank, and Crossfire.

In January 2018 the new line-up of 2Kill Gaming was announced - returning the organization to competitive League of Legends.

